strings: <voice_0x01001C72><se_high>Princess Medea: We've travelled so far during our quest, <hero>.
<voice_0x01001C73><se_high>Princess Medea: Do you really think defeating Dhoulmagus will lift the curse? Do you really think everything will go back to normal?

<voice_0x01001C74><se_high>Princess Medea: I miss Trodain.
I miss the way things were before.
<voice_0x01001C75><se_high>Princess Medea: I don't know how far our journey will take us, but I'll always be right beside you, <hero>.

<voice_0x01001C76><se_high>Princess Medea: You know what I want to do?
Hold hands and walk through the royal garden, just like we used to...
<voice_0x01001C77><se_high>Princess Medea: I hope this will all be over soon...
